Emery on team selection for Real &quot;I want to take more minutes with the players thinking about our progress for the match against Newcastle. But we're going to use some young players at the beginning or during the match to continue trying with this difficult capacity against Real&quot;<br />
<br />
Emery on Real &quot;Maybe the most difficult match [of the tour] &amp; another opportunity for every player to show his capacity. The result isnt the most important, the most important is to use players &amp; have them taking confidence &amp; share minutes between the experienced &amp; young players&quot;
